Package: turbovncui
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3-pyqt6, turbovnc
Description: Graphical frontend for TurboVNC
 TurboVNC UI provides a modern, user-friendly graphical interface
 for managing and launching TurboVNC connections. It allows users
 to create, edit, delete, and connect to VNC servers without
 having to remember command-line syntax.
 .
 Features:
  * Connection management (add, edit, delete)
  * Persistent storage of connection settings
  * One-click connection to VNC servers
  * Remembers last used connection
  * Modern PyQt6-based interface
  * Compatible with XFCE and other desktop environments 